Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, python3-pil, python3-requests
Description: A professional wallpaper manager for Linux desktops
 WallShuffle is a premium, privacy-first wallpaper manager designed for GNOME, KDE, and XFCE.
 It features high-quality Unsplash integration, local image effects (Blur, Sepia, Grayscale),
 and robust multi-monitor support.
